<br>
So she stood. Her eyes continued to stare into space as if she was still in keep thought, though she wasn't. Never once did she offer the figure her gaze or even grace his existance with ackknowledgement. No. He was working. And she was done. And she left. Simple. She walked away through the dark ally and onto the next. <p><br>
