<br>
The fiend took a step. Already her daggers were drawn and the dull end of the blade pressed against her forearm. Weakling! He dared stand against her? He would soon know the price of menising with an angel.<br>
<br>
He ran faster at her now, lunging and attacking. She wouldn't dodge. With an iron force behind it her foot went towards his jaw to kick him back and in a single fluid movement her foot was back on the ground and her arm thrust upward to slice him open with her dagger drawn close at her wrist. This was the sole reason she had been created, this was what she was destined for.  <p><br>
<br>
<br>
